---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="Work" description="Professional background -- from web2 startups to onchain generative art.">
  <div class="page-header">
    <h1>Work</h1>
    <p>The short version of the professional arc.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="work-section">
    <div class="work-role">
      <div class="work-role-header">
        <h2>Art Blocks</h2>
        <span class="work-meta">Chief Product Officer &middot; 2024 &ndash; present</span>
      </div>
      <p>
        Leading product, engineering, design, and community for the platform that defined long-form generative art onchain. Working on the transition from Art Blocks' foundational era to broader adoption -- partnerships, consumer infrastructure, and scaling without losing what made the platform matter in the first place.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="work-role">
      <div class="work-role-header">
        <h2>VenturePunk</h2>
        <span class="work-meta">Founder &amp; CEO &middot; 2022 &ndash; 2024</span>
      </div>
      <p>
        Web3 product studio. Built <strong>Prohibition</strong>, an onchain generative art platform on Arbitrum using Art Blocks Engine, with daily drops on Base. Also founded <strong>Skylab</strong>, a web3 founder community for sharing resources and making introductions across the ecosystem.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="work-role">
      <div class="work-role-header">
        <h2>Nifty's</h2>
        <span class="work-meta">Co-founder &amp; CPO &middot; 2021 &ndash; 2022 &middot; exited to MoonPay</span>
      </div>
      <p>
        Co-founded an NFT platform that partnered with major entertainment brands. Led product and engineering -- launched NFT campaigns with Warner Bros. for The Matrix and Space Jam. Exited to MoonPay.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="work-role">
      <div class="work-role-header">
        <h2>ConsenSys</h2>
        <span class="work-meta">Product Lead, DeFi &middot; 2019 &ndash; 2021</span>
      </div>
      <p>
        Led product teams building early DeFi products and protocols. Also consulted with the MetaMask team on NFT strategy. This is where I went deep on Ethereum infrastructure and started the <strong>$MEME</strong> project -- a pioneering DeFi/NFT experiment that eventually led to co-founding Nifty's.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="work-role">
      <div class="work-role-header">
        <h2>Totle</h2>
        <span class="work-meta">Chief Product Officer &middot; 2018 &ndash; 2019 &middot; acquired by Coinbase</span>
      </div>
      <p>
        Early decentralized exchange aggregator -- think of it as the DEX version of a price comparison engine. Led product strategy and development. Acquired by Coinbase.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="work-role">
      <div class="work-role-header">
        <h2>JibJab</h2>
        <span class="work-meta">Product Lead &middot; 2014 &ndash; 2018</span>
      </div>
      <p>
        Joined after JibJab acquired Hello Santa, a startup I co-founded. Led product for JibJab.com and the iOS app -- which Apple featured in a WWDC keynote. Launched the Android app and ran the digital content strategy.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="work-role">
      <div class="work-role-header">
        <h2>Hello Santa / 4bit Digital</h2>
        <span class="work-meta">Co-founder &middot; 2011 &ndash; 2014 &middot; acquired by JibJab</span>
      </div>
      <p>
        Co-founded 4bit Digital, a web development studio working with NBCUniversal, Panasonic, Public Storage, and others. Spun out Hello Santa -- live one-on-one video calls with Santa Claus. Acquired by JibJab in 2014.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="section" style="margin-top: var(--space-10);">
    <p style="color: var(--color-text-secondary); font-size: 0.875rem;">
      See what I'm <a href="/now/" class="inline-link">working on now</a>,
      <a href="/projects/" class="inline-link">side projects</a>, or
      <a href="/writing/" class="inline-link">what I'm thinking about</a>.
    </p>
  </div>
</Base>

<style>
  .work-section {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-10);
  }

  .work-role-header {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-3);
  }

  .work-role-header h2 {
    margin-top: 0;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-1);
  }

  .work-meta {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    color: var(--color-text-tertiary);
  }

  .work-role p {
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    line-height: 1.65;
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }
</style>
